content:
The Einstein Generative AI automates assessment generation. Home Health optimizes visit scheduling and has a new component for Experience Cloud users. Integrated Care Management integrates with Milliman Care Guidelines (MCG) to bring industry-standard care guidelines and assessments to Health Cloud.

Einstein for Health Cloud harnesses the power of Einstein generative AI to streamline healthcare operations and enhance patient health outcomes. Health Cloud's Assessment Generation leverages Einstein's capabilities to simplify the labor-intensive process of creating assessment questions by efficiently extracting question details from complex documents.

The new integration with Milliman Care Guidelines (MCG) enables Integrated Care Management users to access industry standard care guidelines and make informed decisions on patient care. Administer MCG guidelines-based assessments and create personalized care plans from completed assessments.

The Group Benefits app helps insurance sales agents track leads and enroll members better to boost sales performance. Intelligent Appointment Management now supports multi-step scheduling. Provider Network Management gets a new app.

A new console app has been added to Health Cloud. Changes have been made to how Health Cloud uses the Health Cloud Managed Package. The Patient Segmentation dashboard provides comprehensive insights into patient demographics, risk scores, and health conditions by using segmentation insights to optimize patient care.

Health Cloud includes access to features that are available across clouds and products in Industries. Action Launcher allows contact center agents to quickly resolve customer requests by launching Aura components. Criteria-Based Search and Filter enhances the Provider Search experience for authenticated and guest users. Business Rules Engine incorporates new logic into expression set versions efficiently. Data Processing Engine uploads large amounts of data into your definition with CSV files.

Intelligent Document Reader extracts unstructured content and tables from documents, excluding unwanted records. Intelligent Form Reader does the same.
title: Health Cloud Release Notes
